The paper deals with developing a system that helps users choose criterion weights that lead to greater fairness in ranking items from a database. This involves computing the score of each item as a weighted sum of attribute values and sorting items on their score. This falls under the domains of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
